    {
      "slug": "target/model-architecture.html",
      "title": "复合模型架构与生成流",
      "summary": "拆开复合配置、说话人编码器、Talker、残差码本预测器与目标源码中的 FP32 精度岛。",
      "order": 3,
      "group": "target-architecture",
      "objectives": [
        "解释复合配置如何嵌套 speaker、Talker 与 code predictor",
        "区分 Talker 的 codec-0 输出与 MTP 的 15 个残差码本组",
        "定位 RoPE、RMSNorm 与 eager attention 的 FP32 计算边界"
      ],
      "prerequisites": ["熟悉 PyTorch 单卡张量与自回归生成"],
      "sections": [
        {
          "id": "composite-config",
          "title": "复合配置树",
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "Qwen3-TTS 配置把 speaker encoder、code predictor、Talker 与顶层条件生成配置嵌套在一起；配置树是后续源码导航的结构入口。",
              "state": "verified",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-CONFIG-001"]
            },
            {
              "type": "table",
              "headers": ["组件", "源码路径", "固定范围"],
              "rows": [
                ["复合配置", "qwen_tts/core/models/configuration_qwen3_tts.py", "L22–L499"],
                ["Speaker/Talker/条件生成", "qwen_tts/core/models/modeling_qwen3_tts.py", "L311–L2292"],
                ["speech tokenizer 资源装载", "qwen_tts/core/models/modeling_qwen3_tts.py", "L1891–L1936"]
              ]
            },
            {"type": "source_refs", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-CONFIG-001"]}
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "speaker-encoder",
          "title": "Speaker encoder：mel 到 embedding",
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "Qwen3TTSSpeakerEncoder 是 ECAPA 风格说话人编码器：输入侧契约是 24kHz 音频对应的 128-bin mel，forward 产出 speaker embedding。这里描述类与张量路径，不声称音频已在本机执行。",
              "state": "verified",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-001"]
            },
            {"type": "source_refs", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-001"]}
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "talker",
          "title": "Talker：text+codec 到 codec-0",
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "Qwen3TTSTalkerForConditionalGeneration 把文本与已有 codec 条件送入 decoder，并由 LM head 预测 codec-0 logits。codec-0 是 Talker 的主序列输出，不能与后续残差码本组混为一谈。",
              "state": "verified",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-002"]
            },
            {"type": "source_refs", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-002"]}
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "code-predictor",
          "title": "MTP：15 个残差码本组",
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "code predictor 消费 Talker hidden state 与先前码本条件，补齐 15 个残差码本组；forward_sub_talker_finetune 返回残差码本损失。因而 codec-0 与 15 个残差码本组是两个相邻但不同的职责。",
              "state": "verified",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-004", "TGT-MODEL-002"]
            },
            {"type": "source_refs", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-004", "TGT-MODEL-002"]}
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "precision-islands",
          "title": "目标源码的 FP32 精度岛",
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "目标模型源码中，Talker RoPE 在关闭 autocast 后用 FP32 计算再恢复输入 dtype；RMSNorm 的方差用 FP32；eager attention 的 softmax 用 FP32 再转回 query dtype。这些是官方目标实现的局部精度范围，不是迁移映射。",
              "state": "verified",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-005", "TGT-MODEL-006", "TGT-MODEL-007"]
            },
            {"type": "source_refs", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-005", "TGT-MODEL-006", "TGT-MODEL-007"]}
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "generation-flow",
          "title": "提示词到语音资源的静态生成流",
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "call_chain",
              "items": [
                {"label": "提示词与说话人条件", "path": "qwen_tts/core/models/modeling_qwen3_tts.py", "symbol": "Qwen3TTSForConditionalGeneration", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-003"]},
                {"label": "Talker codec-0", "path": "qwen_tts/core/models/modeling_qwen3_tts.py", "symbol": "Qwen3TTSTalkerForConditionalGeneration", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-003", "TGT-MODEL-002"]},
                {"label": "MTP 残差码本", "path": "qwen_tts/core/models/modeling_qwen3_tts.py", "symbol": "forward_sub_talker_finetune", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-004"]},
                {"label": "语音 tokenizer 与生成配置", "path": "qwen_tts/core/models/modeling_qwen3_tts.py", "symbol": "speech_tokenizer/* + generation_config.json", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-TOK25-011"]}
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "静态阅读顺序是 prompt/说话人条件 → Talker 的 codec-0 → MTP 残差组 → speech_tokenizer/* 与 generation_config.json。资源装载路径存在不等于外部资源已经取得或执行。",
              "state": "verified",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-003", "TGT-TOK25-011"]
            },
            {"type": "source_refs", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-003", "TGT-TOK25-011"]}
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "model-boundary",
          "title": "状态与模型边界",
